Definition: a statement that is assumed to be true and from which a conclusion can be drawn
Example: on the assumption that he has been injured we can infer that he will not play
Synonyms: verb, cognition, premiss, assumption, assume, postulate, a, statement, that, is, assumed, to, be, true, and, from, which, conclusion, can, drawn, on, the, he, has, been, injured, we, infer, will, not, play
Category: noun.communication
